data.description: Experience the best of Reno living in this beautifully renovated 4-bedroom, 3-bath brick charmer home at 1210 Forest St. Boasting 2600 sq feet, this residence is nestled in the heart of the coveted 89509 zip code "the old southwest". Offering a prime midtown location for a vibrant lifestyle. Every sg foot has been renovated inside and out. This is a must see if you are looking for midtown living.
